Definition: without previous thought or preparation
Example: couldn't give the figures offhand; we decided offhand to go to Canada; she had made these remarks offhandedly
Synonyms: offhanded, offhandedly, adj, all, unprepared, without, previous, thought, or, preparation, couldn, t, give, the, figures, we, decided, to, go, Canada, she, had, made, these, remarks
Category: adv.all
